386
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:35,050
♪ Tatandaan ko ang daan pauwi ♪

387
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:43,280
♪ Huwag kang umiyak, huwag kang umiyak ♪

388
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:58,550
kapatid,

389
00:16:59,390 --> 00:17:00,450
Natutunan ko ang tungkol sa

390
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,380
Ang sakit ni tatay.

391
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:07,300
Maging si Lord Ling, sa lahat ng kanyang kakayahan,

392
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,349
walang magawa?

393
00:17:13,349 --> 00:17:13,880
Will Father

394
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:15,160
hindi na magigising muli?

395
00:17:15,839 --> 00:17:16,569
Huwag kang mag-alala.

396
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:19,240
Tiyak na magigising ang kanyang kamahalan.

397
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:21,920
talaga?

398
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:24,829
Suige,

399
00:17:25,510 --> 00:17:27,040
pag gising ni papa,

400
00:17:27,069 --> 00:17:28,490
dapat natin siyang hikayatin

401
00:17:28,550 --> 00:17:29,320
hindi sa

402
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:30,550
magtrabaho nang husto.

403
00:17:35,510 --> 00:17:36,350
alam ko,

404
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,560
hindi mo sinasabi ito nang malakas,

405
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:39,590
ngunit sa kaibuturan,

406
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:41,740
nagmamalasakit ka kay Ama.

407
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:43,880
Saka bakit naman

408
00:17:44,030 --> 00:17:45,880
na sa tuwing magkikita kayong dalawa,

409
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,790
mag-aaway kayo?

410
00:17:49,510 --> 00:17:51,710
May mga bagay na hindi mo maintindihan.

411
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:52,510
At umaasa ako

412
00:17:52,530 --> 00:17:53,560
hinding hindi mo gagawin.

413
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,660
Baka hindi ko maintindihan,

414
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:57,640
pero ako lang

415
00:17:58,350 --> 00:18:00,110
sana kayo ni Ama

416
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:01,240
maaaring magkasundo.

417
00:18:02,110 --> 00:18:02,880
Ngayon na Xiyang

418
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:04,070
Iniwan si Susha,

419
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,310
Si Tatay lang ang meron

420
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:07,570
kaming dalawa sa tabi niya.

421
00:18:13,750 --> 00:18:14,720
Lumaki ka na.

422
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:17,010
Mas matino ngayon.

423
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:38,550
Tiyo!

424
00:18:39,310 --> 00:18:39,960
Tiyo!

425
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,160
Tiyo.

426
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,110
Tiyo.

427
00:18:43,590 --> 00:18:44,350
nakabalik na ako.

428
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,230
Patawarin mo ako, Tiyo.

429
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:57,710
Walang malalakas na boses sa loob ng ancestral hall.

430
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,190
tito,

431
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,000
sa sandaling natanggap ko ang iyong mensahe,

432
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,730
Mabilis akong bumalik sa abot ng aking makakaya.

433
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:13,480
Ngayon lang,

434
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,270
Sobrang saya ko nang makita kita

435
00:19:15,310 --> 00:19:16,840
at medyo nakalimutan ko ang sarili ko.

436
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:18,550
Patawarin mo sana ako.

437
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:28,410
Masaya ka ba?

438
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:33,260
Sa sulat mo, sinabi mo

439
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:34,920
ang matandang iyon na si Feng Pingcheng

440
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:35,750
ay may karamdaman sa wakas.

441
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:37,050
Syempre masaya ako!

442
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:40,000
Nakangiti sa amin si Heaven.

443
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:40,480
Hindi.

444
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:42,510
Si Brother Jingheng
ang nagpapala sa iyo mula sa itaas.

445
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:44,110
Tinutulungan ka niya mula sa itaas!

446
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:49,030
bobong baboy!

447
00:19:49,050 --> 00:19:50,070
bobong baboy!

448
00:19:50,090 --> 00:19:50,790
tanga!

449
00:19:51,070 --> 00:19:51,750
-Gago!
-Tito.

450
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:52,210
tanga!

451
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:52,920
Uncle, sorry.

452
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:53,380
tanga!

453
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:54,160
Patawarin mo ako.

454
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:54,960
tanga!

455
00:19:56,030 --> 00:19:56,720
tito,

456
00:19:58,310 --> 00:19:59,440
at least sabihin mo sa akin

457
00:19:59,510 --> 00:20:00,690
ang mali ko.

458
00:20:01,110 --> 00:20:02,000
Makinig,

459
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,860
Kailangang mamatay si Feng Pingcheng,

460
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,500
pero dapat mamatay siya sa kamay ko!

461
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:07,670
Hindi ako makapaghintay na mapunit siya!

462
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,790
Hindi ko siya papayagan

463
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:09,550
mamatay sa sakit!

464
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:10,510
hindi ako papayag!

465
00:20:12,110 --> 00:20:14,510
Sa lahat ng mga taon
ng pagdadalamhati sa pagkamatay ng aking anak—

466
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:15,480
nanumpa ako

467
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:16,920
para bayaran siya ng isang daang beses,

468
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:17,990
isang libo ulit!

469
00:20:19,110 --> 00:20:19,900
gusto ko siya

470
00:20:20,310 --> 00:20:21,730
para manood ng Feng Suige

471
00:20:21,790 --> 00:20:23,520
mamatay nang malungkot sa harap ng kanyang mga mata.

472
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,730
Gusto kong lumuhod siya sa paanan ko

473
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:28,010
nagmamakaawa sa akin na iligtas ang buhay ni Feng Suige!

474
00:20:29,140 --> 00:20:30,210
Sa lahat ng mga taon na ito,

475
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:33,240
Ini-imagine ko ang araw

476
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,350
noong si Feng Pingcheng, matanda at kulay abo,

477
00:20:34,350 --> 00:20:35,640
inililibing ang kanyang batang anak.

478
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:37,560
gusto ko...

479
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:38,880
Gusto ko siyang makitang nabubuhay

480
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,000
sa impyerno gamit ang sarili kong mga mata.

481
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:42,000
Paano ko siya hahayaang mamatay sa sakit?

482
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,060
Pinapabalik kita

483
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:47,080
kasi may task ako sayo.

484
00:20:52,510 --> 00:20:54,110
Hinihintay ko ang utos mo, Tiyo.

485
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:56,270
Limang araw na siyang walang malay.

486
00:20:56,270 --> 00:20:58,130
Hindi ko siya hahayaang mamatay ng ganito.

487
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:01,570
Dapat kang makahanap ng paraan sa anumang halaga

488
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:04,360
para magising siya.

489
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:05,970
Kahit na ang ibig sabihin nito ay lason,

490
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,130
dapat gisingin mo siya!

491
00:21:07,590 --> 00:21:08,070
gusto ko siya

492
00:21:08,070 --> 00:21:09,270
upang maging ganap na mulat

493
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:11,070
nang makita niya si Feng Suige

494
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,830
magdusa at mamatay!

495
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,000
Naintindihan.

496
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:29,620
[Memorial Tablet of My Late Tita Wang]

497
00:21:29,670 --> 00:21:32,590
[Kagalingan ng Ninuno at Merito ng Pamilya]

498
00:21:59,350 --> 00:21:59,920
Ama.

499
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:07,870
Bakit ka bumalik?

500
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,600
Dalawang araw na lang ang kaarawan mo.

501
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:10,750
Syempre kailangan kong bumalik

502
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:11,810
para ipagdiwang ito kasama ka.

503
00:22:11,810 --> 00:22:12,680
Palihim akong bumalik

504
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,360
para ma-surprise ka lang.

505
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:17,440
Abala ka
sa mga usaping militar diyan,

506
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:18,590
paglilingkod sa bansa.

507
00:22:18,590 --> 00:22:20,450
Nakakaproud na yun.

