Binabati kita, Kamahalan.

753
00:34:30,110 --> 00:34:32,440
Ang kanyang kamahalan ay nagsilang ng isang prinsesa.

754
00:34:32,590 --> 00:34:34,449
Binabati kita, Kamahalan.

755
00:34:35,110 --> 00:34:35,800
Kahanga-hanga.

756
00:34:36,510 --> 00:34:38,370
Binabati kita, Kamahalan.

757
00:34:38,670 --> 00:34:39,670
Ngayon, Kamahalan

758
00:34:39,670 --> 00:34:41,190
ay may isang anak na lalaki at isang anak na babae.

759
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:41,989
Oo, talaga.

