Kamahalan.

761
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,800
isang araw,

762
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:45,670
Magtitiis din ako

763
00:34:45,670 --> 00:34:47,270
isang prinsipe para sa iyo, kung nais mo.

764
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:49,150
Syempre.

765
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,440
Tara puntahan natin si Empress.

766
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:04,290
Pagbati, Kamahalan.

767
00:35:07,590 --> 00:35:09,650
Hindi pa nakakain ng hapunan ang kanyang Kamahalan.

768
00:35:09,670 --> 00:35:10,230
Nakaupo siya doon

769
00:35:10,230 --> 00:35:11,230
sa loob ng ilang oras

770
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:12,740
nang walang sabi-sabi.

771
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:20,170
Anong ginagawa mo dito?

772
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:21,920
Gabi na kasi.

773
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:23,510
Bakit gising ka pa?

774
00:35:24,230 --> 00:35:25,070
nanay,

775
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,460
ingatan mo ang sarili mo.

776
00:35:27,550 --> 00:35:28,810
Huwag masyadong magdalamhati.

777
00:35:41,560 --> 00:35:49,700
[Murong Residence]

778
00:35:46,030 --> 00:35:47,560
Kuya Marquis, nakauwi na kami.

779
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,260
Kuya Marquis?

780
00:35:53,230 --> 00:35:54,090
Elder Marquis.

781
00:35:56,040 --> 00:35:57,600
Si Elder Marquis ay nawawala!

782
00:35:57,620 --> 00:35:59,570
Ano ang dapat nating gawin ngayon?

783
00:36:02,550 --> 00:36:03,580
Anong nangyari?

784
00:36:03,870 --> 00:36:04,800
Paano nawala ang aking ama

785
00:36:04,800 --> 00:36:05,860
pagkatapos ng isang biyahe palabas?

786
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:06,760
ako…

787
00:36:06,810 --> 00:36:08,110
Wala talaga akong alam.

788
00:36:08,130 --> 00:36:09,510
Inabot kami ng mahigit isang oras bago kami makabalik

789
00:36:09,510 --> 00:36:10,760
mula sa mansyon ni Punong Ministro Zhuang.

790
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:12,030
Tiningnan ko ang karwahe pagdating namin,

791
00:36:12,030 --> 00:36:13,000
at ang Elder Marquis ay

792
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,340
wala na.

793
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:15,630
Pag-isipang mabuti.

794
00:36:15,710 --> 00:36:17,280
May kakaiba bang nangyari sa daan?

795
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:19,210
Bukod sa isang baka na nakaharang sa kalsada…

796
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:23,710
Bumaba ako at inakay ito.

797
00:36:23,810 --> 00:36:25,320
Walang ibang nangyari.

798
00:36:27,510 --> 00:36:28,760
Pagkatapos ilipat ang baka,

799
00:36:28,790 --> 00:36:29,710
sinuri mo ba kung tatay ko

800
00:36:29,710 --> 00:36:31,110
nasa karwahe pa ba?

801
00:36:31,110 --> 00:36:32,090
Hindi.

802
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:34,240
Wala akong narinig na tunog,

803
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:35,580
kaya naisip ko

804
00:36:35,630 --> 00:36:36,830
siya ay nakatulog.

805
00:36:41,440 --> 00:36:42,760
Saan mo nakita ang baka?

806
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:43,800
Nakaraan sa Yudai Bridge,

807
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:45,330
sa ikatlong intersection.

808
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:45,920
tama,

809
00:36:45,920 --> 00:36:47,850
may baluktot na puno sa tabi ng kalsada.

810
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:53,590
Hanapin ang bawat bahay

811
00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:54,650
sa lugar na iyon.

812
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:55,880
Kahit na kailangan nating iikot ang Yujing City

813
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:56,360
baligtad,

814
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,290
kailangan natin siyang mahanap!

815
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:57,920
Oo.

816
00:37:01,280 --> 00:37:02,190
Fu Yixiao,

817
00:37:02,230 --> 00:37:03,320
Alam kong ikaw iyon.

818
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:04,960
Kapag nahuli kita,

819
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:06,960
Balatan kita ng buhay

820
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:08,290
at hiwa-hiwain ka!

821
00:37:17,670 --> 00:37:18,360
sino ka ba

822
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,230
How dare you

823
00:37:20,230 --> 00:37:21,190
dukutin ako

824
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:22,990
sa ilalim mismo ng ilong ng Emperador?

825
00:37:23,710 --> 00:37:24,880
Hindi nakakagulat na ikaw

826
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:26,520
isang matigas na labanan na marquis.

827
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,520
Kahit nasa panganib,

828
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:29,760
kalmado ka

829
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:30,960
at walang takot.

830
00:37:33,110 --> 00:37:34,920
Kaya alam mo kung sino ako.

831
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:37,440
Mukhang ikaw ang aking kaaway,

832
00:37:38,070 --> 00:37:39,530
pero hindi kita nakikilala.

833
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:42,110
Ilang dekada akong nagbabantay sa mga hangganan,

834
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:43,570
pakikipaglaban sa hindi mabilang na digmaan.

835
00:37:43,590 --> 00:37:45,630
Mas marami na akong naging kaaway na hindi ko mabilang.

836
00:37:45,630 --> 00:37:47,150
Aling panig ka?

837
00:37:47,280 --> 00:37:49,000
Anong sama ng loob mo sa akin?

838
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:49,920
Sige, sabihin mo na.

839
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:50,880
Todo tenga ako.

840
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:54,280
Mga taon na nakatalaga sa nagyeyelong hilaga

841
00:37:54,550 --> 00:37:56,080
iniwan ang iyong mga binti sa masamang hugis.

842
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,320
At gayon pa man,

843
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:58,800
Hindi
ka pa rin pinayagan ng kanyang kamahalan na umuwi

844
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:00,260
upang tamasahin ang iyong pagreretiro.

845
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:01,800
Kaya ba ang pamilya Murong

846
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:03,190
napopoot sa Kanyang Kamahalan?

847
00:38:05,070 --> 00:38:05,880
yun lang?

848
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:09,280
Ni hindi ko alam
kung ano ang sinasabi mo.

849
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:11,770
Ang aking katapatan sa Kanyang Kamahalan

850
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,000
ay kasing linaw ng araw.

851
00:38:13,670 --> 00:38:15,840
Hindi ko kailanman kinasusuklaman ang Kanyang Kamahalan.

852
00:38:16,590 --> 00:38:18,190
Kung gayon bakit ang iyong anak, si Murong Yao,

853
00:38:18,190 --> 00:38:19,460
nagbabalak ng pag-aalsa?

854
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:36,210
Mukhang hindi ka naniniwala sa akin.

855
00:38:38,150 --> 00:38:39,900
Sumali ako sa hukbo noong bata pa ako

856
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:41,710
at gumugol ng mga dekada sa larangan ng digmaan.

857
00:38:41,710 --> 00:38:42,550
Wala kang ideya

858
00:38:42,550 --> 00:38:43,400
ilang tao

859
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:45,960
sinubukan akong i-frame para sa pagtataksil

860
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,150
sa harap ng Kanyang Kamahalan.

861
00:38:47,510 --> 00:38:49,170
Kung sisiraan mo ako,

862
00:38:49,590 --> 00:38:51,590
at least makabuo ng bago.

863
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,510
Si Yao ay nagbabalak ng paghihimagsik?

864
00:38:55,510 --> 00:38:57,420
Oo naman, siya ay palaging isang dakot,

865
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,800
pero never ko siyang inisip

866
00:38:58,800 --> 00:39:00,140
bilang ambisyoso.

867
00:39:00,670 --> 00:39:02,710
I actually wish na iba siya

868
00:39:02,730 --> 00:39:03,670
kaya ayaw niya

869
00:39:03,670 --> 00:39:05,280
gumugol araw-araw sa kahalayan

870
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:06,340
at sayangin ang kanyang buhay.

871
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:09,280
Akalain mo hindi ko pa sinubukang humila ng mga string

872
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:11,480
para sa kanya sa hukbo at hukuman?

873
00:39:11,780 --> 00:39:13,040
Tumanggi lang siya.

874
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:15,070
Hindi man lang siya kukuha ng opisyal na posisyon,

875
00:39:15,070 --> 00:39:17,150
pero sinasabi mong may balak siyang mutiny?

876
00:39:17,150 --> 00:39:18,190
Ito ang pinakamalaking biro

877
00:39:18,190 --> 00:39:19,480
Narinig ko buong taon!

878
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:22,070
Nakipagsabwatan si Murong Yao kay Jinxiu

879
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:23,710
upang patayin ang Unang Prinsipe.

880
00:39:23,710 --> 00:39:24,640
alam mo ba kung ano?

881
00:39:28,070 --> 00:39:29,510
Ngayon alam ko na kung sino ka.

882
00:39:30,550 --> 00:39:32,280
Ikaw ang babaeng heneral mula sa Jinxiu—

883
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,550
isa sa mga tao ni Suige.

884
00:39:34,710 --> 00:39:36,570
Inakusahan ng isang heneral ng Jinxiu si Yao

885
00:39:36,590 --> 00:39:39,190
ng pakikipagsabwatan kay Jinxiu?

886
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:41,230
Isang pasaway na playboy

887
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:43,030
mula sa isang marangal na pamilya

888
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:44,110
sinong umiikot

889
00:39:44,110 --> 00:39:45,670
kasama ang apat na magagandang assassin—

890
00:39:45,670 --> 00:39:47,000
sino ang gusto niyang patayin?

891
00:39:47,760 --> 00:39:48,960
Alam mo ba talaga

892
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:50,350
sarili mong anak?

893
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:52,070
alam mo ba

894
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,280
kung sino ang nakakasama niya

895
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:54,360
at sino ang nasa paligid niya?

896
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,590
Palagi kang wala sa hangganan.

897
00:39:55,590 --> 00:39:56,960
Alam mo ba talaga kung ano ang ginagawa niya

898
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:58,000
dito sa Yujing?

899
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:01,440
Tinatawag mo ang iyong sarili
na pinaka-tapat na opisyal sa korte,

900
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:02,320
pero sigurado ka bang anak mo

901
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:03,180
kasing loyal mo?

902
00:40:03,510 --> 00:40:04,360
Kung siya talaga

903
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:05,070
ilang playboy

904
00:40:05,070 --> 00:40:06,670
walang ambisyon tulad ng sinabi mo,

905
00:40:06,670 --> 00:40:07,550
bakit niya kinuha ang trabaho

906
00:40:07,550 --> 00:40:09,010
kasama ang Imperial Guards?

907
00:40:10,590 --> 00:40:12,790
Iyon ay inayos ng Kanyang Kamahalan.

908
00:40:12,860 --> 00:40:14,170
Ikaw lang nagsabi sa sarili mo

909
00:40:14,590 --> 00:40:15,630
na sa buong buhay niya,

910
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:17,400
hindi siya sumunod sa utos.

911
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:19,320
Siya…

912
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:23,320
anak ko…

913
00:40:25,510 --> 00:40:26,910
Naaawa lang ako sayo.

914
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:27,960
Noon, nag-away kayo

915
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:28,940
kasama ng Kanyang Kamahalan

916
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:30,200
at nauwi sa lahat ng mga pinsalang ito.

917
00:40:30,200 --> 00:40:31,360
Alam na alam ito ng Kanyang Kamahalan,

918
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:32,550
kaya bakit ka pa niya pinadala sa malamig na iyon,

919
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:34,280
baog na lugar sa hilagang-kanluran?

920
00:40:37,150 --> 00:40:38,150
Murong Yao at Feng Suige

921
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:39,680
ay ang pinakamalapit sa mga kaibigan.

922
00:40:39,880 --> 00:40:41,080
Pero binantaan niya ako,

923
00:40:41,290 --> 00:40:42,320
sabi sa mukha ko

924
00:40:42,630 --> 00:40:43,510
na kung sasabihin ko man kay Feng Suige

925
00:40:43,510 --> 00:40:44,360
ang kanyang sikreto,

926
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:45,690
gagawa siya ng paraan

927
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:46,630
upang patayin si Feng Pingcheng,

928
00:40:46,630 --> 00:40:48,630
na ngayon ay nakahiga sa kama sa palasyo.

929
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:51,400
Wala akong pakialam
kung mabuhay o mamatay si Feng Pingcheng.

930
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:53,180
Pero hindi ako papayag kahit kanino

931
00:40:53,230 --> 00:40:54,290
para saktan si Feng Suige.

932
00:40:55,840 --> 00:40:56,630
Imposible!

933
00:40:58,030 --> 00:41:00,290
Hindi kailanman sasabihin ni Yao ang ganoong bagay.

934
00:41:00,510 --> 00:41:01,960
Siya at si Suige

935
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:03,910
sabay lumaki na parang magkapatid!

936
00:41:04,150 --> 00:41:06,030
Hinding-hindi siya gagawa ng pagtataksil!

937
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:08,230
Kahit anong paraan mayroon si Murong Yao

938
00:41:08,230 --> 00:41:09,590
pagbabanta kay Feng Pingcheng,

939
00:41:09,590 --> 00:41:11,150
hangga't may kontrol ako sa iyo,

940
00:41:11,150 --> 00:41:12,030
May tiwala ako

941
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:13,680
hindi siya maglalakas loob na gumawa ng hakbang.

942
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:15,300
Elder Marquis,

943
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,400
humihingi ako ng tawad.

944
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:29,090
masama ba ang pakiramdam mo?

945
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,760
-Ayos ka lang ba?
-Kamahalan.

946
00:41:31,760 --> 00:41:33,160
Bakit ang dami mong iniinom?

947
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:35,670
Maaari ka bang kumuha ng tuwalya,
Kamahalan?

948
00:41:35,670 --> 00:41:36,600
Hintayin mo ako dito.

949
00:41:46,190 --> 00:41:47,150
Nakita mo ba si Wang Encheng

950
00:41:47,150 --> 00:41:47,880
ngayon lang?

951
00:41:48,710 --> 00:41:49,320
Oo.

952
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:51,190
Minarkahan mo ang kanyang pangalan

953
00:41:51,190 --> 00:41:52,520
sa Daily Chronicle.

954
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:54,030
At tinitingnan din niya ang bahagi.

955
00:41:54,630 --> 00:41:57,070
Matagal ko nang narinig ang tungkol sa
mga kakaibang katangian ni Xia Jingyan.

956
00:41:57,070 --> 00:41:57,960
Hindi ko lang naisip

957
00:41:57,960 --> 00:41:59,550
na ang binanggit ng Daily Chronicle

958
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:01,110
tungkol sa kanyang mga gawain sa mga asawa ng mga opisyal

959
00:42:01,110 --> 00:42:02,170
ay talagang totoo.

960
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:03,280
That Wang Encheng—

961
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,190
tingnan mo kung makakahanap ka ng paraan

962
00:42:04,190 --> 00:42:05,250
para makalapit sa kanya.

963
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:06,230
Oo.

964
00:42:07,110 --> 00:42:07,710
nga pala,

965
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:09,110
nung pumasok kami kanina,

966
00:42:09,110 --> 00:42:10,640
may nakabantay ba?

967
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:12,860
Dalawang eunuch lang ang nanatili doon.

968
00:42:13,070 --> 00:42:14,230
Kamukha ni Xia Jingyan

969
00:42:14,230 --> 00:42:16,160
tunay na naniniwalang naisumite mo.

970
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:18,340
Hindi mo siya naiintindihan.

971
00:42:19,360 --> 00:42:21,150
Ang pag-alis ng mga guwardiya
ay paraan lamang niya upang subukan ako.

